      </group>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-DABEA5C2-7FCF-4D05-8DCE-8C067BBD762B" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>1. User awareness required that on which LE the sales order should be placed. If it is placed on the wrong LE, it needs to be cancelled and customer to place the PO on right LE.  OTC will own this.
Intel Foundry Corp – US
Intel Foundry Services Ltd – LE798
2. Same Customer IDs can be extended to both LEs. 

3. Bailed Material will be in Intel Foundry inventory (or ASN for In-Transit) before order is confirmed.
Receiving process is explained on previous slide. 

4. If complete Bailed material stock is not with IF yet, partial order confirmation will happen based on bailed inventory available against Blanket PO.
</text>
      </textAnnotation>
   </process>
